name: Sibling Mirroral
description:
Sibling Mirroral

Root of the mirror is a place where you find your twin. Similar, but not the same. You see many colors of him. Likewise, according to him. There are so many of your colors that don't look the same as hers. What does it mean? Sometimes you only know some of your colors. And for the colors you don't see, it's very clear to the eyes of the others.
